      "kind": "bullet",
      "text": "Despite the fact, that JSON structures can be processed by the C family of programming languages quite easily, there should be a benefit in having some kind of &lt;em&gt;XPath4JSON&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;So I was thinking about a suitable path expression syntax for addressing portions of any JSON structure.",
